text: WSIQ is an AM radio station licensed to Salem, Illinois and broadcasting on the frequency of 1350 kHz. The format for WSIQ is Country music and is known as Q 92.1. Previous call letters were WJBD (AM) and are still used for the FM station.http://www.nrgmedia.com/markets/ ==FM Translator== WSIQ can also be heard at 92.1 MHz.
